sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>(HAProxy)<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy sidecar<br/>(head pod)<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>(head pod localhost)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Operator as CodeFlare Operator<br/>(controller-manager)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InitCert as create-cert<br/>init container
    participant HeadNode as Ray Head Node<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant Worker as Ray Worker Node<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant RayClient as Ray Client

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: Ray Dashboard Access (OpenShift)
        User->>Router: GET https://ray-dashboard-{cluster}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward (TLS reencrypt)<br/>HTTPS/8443, OpenShift OAuth token
        OAuthProxy->>Dashboard: Proxy to localhost<br/>HTTP/8265 (no auth, proxied)
        Dashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard HTML/API response
        OAuthProxy-->>Router: Encrypted response
        Router-->>User: HTTPS response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Operator,Worker: Flow 2: RayCluster mTLS Certificate Generation
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create CA Secret (ca-secret-{cluster})<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: CA Secret created (RSA 2048-bit, 1yr)
        Note over InitCert: Pod starts with init container
        InitCert->>InitCert: Generate per-pod TLS cert<br/>signed by cluster CA<br/>Write to /home/ray/workspace/tls
        Note over HeadNode,Worker: Ray nodes start with mTLS enabled (RAY_USE_TLS=1)
        HeadNode->>Worker: gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS (cluster CA)<br/>Client certificate auth
        Worker-->>HeadNode: mTLS encrypted response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over RayClient,HeadNode: Flow 3: Ray Client Connection (OpenShift)
        RayClient->>Router: Connect to rayclient-{cluster}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS passthrough<br/>mTLS client cert
        Router->>HeadNode: Forward (TLS passthrough)<br/>gRPC/10001, mTLS (cluster CA)
        HeadNode-->>Router: gRPC response (mTLS)
        Router-->>RayClient: Encrypted response
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Operator Reconciliation Loop
        K8sAPI->>Operator: RayCluster CR watch event
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update OAuth Service<br/>ServiceAccount, ClusterRoleBinding
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Routes<br/>(dashboard reencrypt, client passthrough)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update NetworkPolicies<br/>(head + worker isolation)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update CA Secret<br/>Cookie Secret
    end
